ClassDesc: List of common, named color spaces. A corresponding instance of @B_android#graphics#ColorSpace_E@ can be obtained by calling @B_android#graphics#ColorSpace#get_E@: The properties of each color space are described below (see @B_android#graphics#ColorSpace#Named#SRGB_E@ for instance). When applicable, the color gamut of each color space is compared to the color gamut of sRGB using a CIE 1931 xy chromaticity diagram. This diagram shows the location of the color space's primaries and white point.
